Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toys 那是被选中的人心中鼓起的奇迹的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人会开出纯洁的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦有的人会开出毒花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大侦探时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争奇斗艳的两朵鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为侦探以及怪盗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是横浜警察引以为傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对怪盗事件调查组Genius4(天才4人组)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称G4的明智小衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.23,c,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}江户川乱步的《少年侦探团》\N系列中登场的名侦探“明智小五郎”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个傻瓜明智
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小衣衣 是我夏洛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…想让我们看的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说怪盗亚森发出了犯罪预告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盗亚森可是连那Milky Holmes都抓不住她哦 你有自信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milky Holmes？别拿我们和那些废柴相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盗亚森肯定由我们G4来抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废柴们就在阁楼里啃零食去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安利艾特大人的目的就是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Milky Holmes体会到自己的无能 让她们的自尊粉粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是安利艾特大人 既优秀又美丽的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 让她知道到底谁才是废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 让我们去抓住她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的是傻到没救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺材的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小衣衣 我看了电视了哦 你真上镜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我小衣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又踩在这上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好对待美术品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你们到底是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扯上怪盗的话 侦探就有保护国宝的浜之维纳斯权利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有Toys的人就没有权利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Toys恢复了的那就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错就是这个 让Toys恢复的方法我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toys存在于历史的阴影中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把海分成两半的摩西的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古埃及的米拉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就已经有了Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些秘密只能被接触法老石碑的人所知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么继续了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手 蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脚 黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手 绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右脚 红色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子真的能找回Toys？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小衣衣的话绝对不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G4的大脑 13岁从哈佛大学毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为天才的明智小衣没有读不懂的字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种字读得懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子为了让发烧降下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去超市的时候偶然间碰到了高中时交往过的悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…果然智商1300是真货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我说的做的话 石板上的暗号就能解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小衣真是好亲切啊 特地告诉她们恢复Toys的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了报以往妨碍她的仇咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小衣老师 知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人左脚 蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像Toys回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我从刚才开始也有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得身体渐渐变热了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连艾莉也？ 说起来我也感觉身体吱吱作响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手 绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色 绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗 不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 已经和那样的家伙分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了说了 手脚以外的部分接触到了石板的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号就无法解读了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右脚 蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样把右脚移到蓝色的话 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 干嘛下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜 Toys消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小衣 差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾 就差一点Toys就能恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.44,c,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}高木彬光笔下的推理小说的主人公“神津恭介”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.24,c,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}江户时代实际存在过的纵火打劫的盗贼“火付盗賊改方”\N以及池波正太郎的小说《鬼平犯科帳》中的主人公“長谷川平蔵”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:07:59.95,c,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}江户时代实际存在过的捕快“遠山金四郎景元”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也配置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 就差那么一点了 为什么没按明智说的做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是只要Toys能过回来的话 多么害羞的事都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这么无法取回Toys的话你要怎么负起这责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了就这样吧 艾莉也知道自己错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 回去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真黑啊 这么黑 就用我的灼热把这里照亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊 怪盗亚森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的是还真是华丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天肯定要抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 柯蒂妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕黑暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 好像有什么要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 幽灵什么的出来也不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别说这种奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻惑的Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点点灯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那里的光照亮这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 浜之维纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们肯定还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 在朝南出口逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊 好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是亚森大人 用幻惑的Toys
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只让浜之维纳斯看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国宝 浜之维纳斯 到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也就现在能够高兴高兴了 发信器怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了 柯蒂妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嘞 这里是？ 她们去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能找到他们的位置了
