Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没讲错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
